BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:kxvXS80bz4XwSOS-GlReY
SUMMARY:7 Week Animal Sculpture
DTSTAMP:20260413T010453Z
DTSTART:20260423T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Explore creating animals through sculpture. Beginning with smal
	l maquettes\\\, we’ll study a variety of techniques for both wall pieces a
	nd free-standing sculptures. Bring your imagination\; animal forms can be 
	personal\\\, mythical or fanciful. \\nYou will apply various hand-building
	 techniques to form clay\\\, including: pinch\\\, slab\\\, coil building a
	nd carving. Students will also have the opportunity to build functional wa
	re for their furry friends.\n\nhttps://discovermagnolia.org/event/7-week-a
	nimal-sculpture/\n\nFrom Discover Magnolia
URL:https://discovermagnolia.org/event/7-week-animal-sculpture/
LOCATION:Gather Pottery\\\, 1465 Elliott Ave W\\\, Seattle\\\, 98119\\\, Un
	ited States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:discover-magnolia
CATEGORIES:Discover Magnolia
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:LzXMfKEP1W0wS-03K3Zpp
SUMMARY:Just Shred It!
DTSTAMP:20260413T010453Z
DTSTART:20260425T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:April 25\\\, 2026\; Just Shred IT! 10 AM to 1 PM\\\, KeyBank pa
	rking lot\\\, W. McGraw St and 34th Ave W. \\nEnter off W. McGraw St.     
	All Residences and Businesses are invited to bring their important papers 
	\\nto be commercially shredded. Save time and effort while gaining peace o
	f mind that your important papers and information are disposed of in a saf
	e and professional manner.  Old tax records\\\, old files\\\, save time an
	d effort.  A $10 donation per box/bag is suggested.  Donations benefit our
	 501 (c) (3) Rotary Club of Magnolia Charitable Foundation.  We will provi
	de you a tax receipt. First come first served. \\nQuestions\\\, please con
	tact Bryce McWalter\\\, 206-283-2037 or info@magnoliarotary.org.\n\nhttps:
	//discovermagnolia.org/event/just-shred-it-5/\n\nFrom Discover Magnolia
URL:https://discovermagnolia.org/event/just-shred-it-5/
LOCATION:Key Bank\\\, 2401 34th Ave W\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98199\\\, Unit
	ed States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:discover-magnolia
CATEGORIES:Discover Magnolia
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
